{"tid":1463284,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方指女子遭射爆眼「眾說紛紜」不掛除邀落口供後作拘捕","createTime":"2019-08-13T12:37:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T13:07:38.000Z","uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"befc95f6e4b1e5e14f573f7a52bc818b6273d0a3","tid":1463284,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:37:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/200954406608272/posts/2367248219978869/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F200954406608272%2Fposts%2F2367248219978869%2F&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2BlNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=25da6cf9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/200954406608272/posts/2367248219978869/</a><br />\n<br />\n有女子被警方槍擊致右眼視力嚴重受損，之後更發現該女生的眼睪上留有布袋彈。有組織罪案及三合會調查科高級警司李桂華回應事件，指現階段「眾說紛紜」，不承認女生受傷與警方有關。<br />\n<br />\n李桂華又稱已邀請該名女生報警落口供。有記者擔心警方在落取口供之後會反控告少女暴動罪，李未有否認，只承諾「落口供之前唔會告佢」。<br />\n<br />\n【警怨市民情緒激動阻執法 籲諒解互相合作】<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2YZeylT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2YZeylT&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2BlNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=47130b30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2YZeylT</a><br />\n<br />\n#獨媒報導<br />\n追蹤最新消息：<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/inmediahknet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Finmediahknet&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2BlNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=d489fe12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/inmediahknet</a><br />\n報導有價，請月捐支持<br />\n<a href=\"http://inmediahk.net/donate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finmediahk.net%2Fdonate&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2BlNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=6ae1e647\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Finmediahk.net%2Fdonate&h=5011d3a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">inmediahk.net/donate</a>"},{"pid":"6a1af3c34691ef1c7d90362626bbe60c6bab8a1b","tid":1463284,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:40:10.00